title: Huge Star Wars Battlefront Scam...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be the Battlefront Classic Collection completely imploding upon release with only three servers and a whole litany of technical problems. It's a shame to say this kind of stuff doesn't even surprise me anymore. Thanks for watching!
